<para>connection string parameter which is transfered to <link linkend="da/dd3/classmpx_1_1_mpx_task_multiplexer">MpxTaskMultiplexer</link> unchanged and it is not examined by this function $param isWorker working thread indicator transferred to <link linkend="da/dd3/classmpx_1_1_mpx_task_multiplexer">MpxTaskMultiplexer</link> constructor </para>
